#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=-Pl0Y6_FewkQ7kNvwGvVtKL&_nc_oc=Adn1A2ZbQdyzPGfiL6zh_VqOMFSGvesopHdXtYBpBcs3s1hVuPiBsjDf3xDiQ8fdXBU&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=VTYipiGggNOALAT1mC3wRg&oh=00_AfpmKpKINaU22SawlhIxTrwsVkKD-FPOstFfShyY0rueNQ&oe=697E01A4)

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=3jI0_5IozlsQ7kNvwFZYpPX&_nc_oc=Adnrwzrw-Qa-GXfGuQM6A4f6vYhm7qNvMpRZQzCy4yG5TmoW0Ozu5I23WMP2fjixqfc&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=VTYipiGggNOALAT1mC3wRg&oh=00_AfruvJtO8gqF2y2_fBr3XlyKBmcXdf_bAB2g5va6FsbpGA&oe=697DF6CC)

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!
